---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
import Pulse from "./Pulse.astro";
---
<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-2">
  <div class="flex justify-between w-full items-start mb-2">
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <h2>Now</h2>
      <a href="https://sive.rs/now" target="_blank">
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 cursor-pointer">what's that?</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <Pulse />
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <p class="text-xs">Leading IT & System Integration at a Tier-1 semiconductor company in Hsinchu, Taiwan.</p>
    <p class="text-xs">Building <b class="font-semibold">The Council</b> — a personal multi-LLM operations setup wired together with n8n, Telegram bots, and too many late nights.</p>
    <p class="text-xs">Working on: Obsidian knowledge system, personal AI pipelines, and this website.</p>
  </div>
</Card>
